 # The writeup ‚Äî a truth layer for agentic commerce
 
-*Publication draft (Pub slice, plan ¬ß5). Written 2026-07-06; all dates and claims are as-of that day and source-backed in `docs/research/` (source lockfile included). This document is the postable narrative; the repo README is the technical front door. Human-led, AI-assisted, professionally reviewed.*
