+> Status note (updated 2026-07-10): this describes the legacy prototype as built. The live Gemini run is **done and recorded** (a frozen fixture; the public demo stays REPLAY-only ‚Äî no live calls). The **deploy happened** (2026-07-08, static site, run-on-demand) and the repo is public (2026-07-09); the deployed site currently still serves this legacy module's console surfaces alongside the truth-audit report/demo, with an explicit identity separation planned. Honesty is itself a why (last section).
 
 ---
 
 ## The problem & the solution
 
-**Why this problem ‚Äî stalled / pre-live, long-tail merchant activation.** A delivery marketplace's signed-up-but-never-live merchants are real lost GMV, and the long tail is too large to work by hand. *Rejected:* generic "AI for merchants" / churn-prevention for *live* merchants. *Cost of that choice:* it's commodity (Gainsight, ChurnZero, DoorDash's own AI Marketer all do outreach) and doesn't fit the pre-live cohort, where the job is *diagnosis*, not retention.
+**Why this problem ‚Äî stalled / pre-live, long-tail merchant activation.** A delivery marketplace's signed-up-but-never-live merchants are real lost GMV, and the long tail is too large to work by hand. *Rejected:* generic "AI for merchants" / churn-prevention for *live* merchants. *Cost of that choice:* it's commodity ‚Äî established customer-success vendors and the marketplaces' own AI outreach suites all do outreach (named, dated citations in `docs/research/market-validation-2026-06-22.md`) ‚Äî and doesn't fit the pre-live cohort, where the job is *diagnosis*, not retention.
 
 **Why this solution ‚Äî diagnose *why* a merchant is stuck, then draft the right next outreach, safely.** The defensible value is the *combination* applied to this vertical, with auditability. *Rejected:* a pure outreach-drafting tool. *Cost:* the research's #1 reactivation-failure cause is **generic outreach not matched to the actual blocker** ‚Äî a drafter without diagnosis ships the exact failure mode. So the diagnosis layer, not the generator, is where the value concentrates.
 
-**Why not just use the incumbents.** DoorDash's May-2026 AI suite auto-fills menu/photos/hours at the source. *Rejected:* competing on photo-fixing. *Cost:* that's being commoditized away. Our edge is **cross-blocker diagnosis + routing + the platform-side cases auto-fill can't touch** ‚Äî and being safe enough to adopt.
